# MMO001 Workflow

## Before coding

1. Pick next unchecked item in [TODO.md](../../TODO.md) (“Next tasks” section)
2. Plan scope; one item per branch (`feature/<name>` or `fix/<name>`)
3. Promote `PENDINGS.md` notes into TODO before implementing (PENDINGS is gitignored)

Post-MVP phase: playtesting fixes and UX polish (v3.3.0+).

## Git

- Branch from `main`; merge when complete, tested, smoke-tested
- **Commit + push** (user asks only): `./scripts/commit-and-push.sh "why-focused message"`
- Never force-push `main`; never commit `.env` or secrets
- No GitHub Actions CI — run `npm test` locally
- Do not add `.github/workflows/` unless user wants CI (OAuth `workflow` scope)

Full merge, deploy, and semver details → [mmo-feature-development/reference.md](../skills/mmo-feature-development/reference.md)

## On merge

1. Bump [package.json](../../package.json) (patch = fix, minor = feature)
2. Update [CHANGELOG.md](../../CHANGELOG.md) and check off [TODO.md](../../TODO.md)
3. Update [README.md](../../README.md) if controls or setup changed

